  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"βασιλ εὺς Μαστέαβαρ βασιλέος Γαυου\"><span data-text=\"βασιλ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">[βασιλ]</span>  <span data-text=\"εὺς\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">εὺς</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαστέαβαρ\"><span data-text=\"Μαστέαβαρ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">Μαστέαβαρ</span></span>  <span data-text=\"βασιλέος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">βασιλέος</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γαυου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Γαυου\"><span data-text=\"Γαυου\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">Γαυου</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Σ̣Π̣Ο̣ <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Υ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Π[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΕΥ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Γ̣ΕΙΑΝ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Λ̣ΟΥ <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Ε <br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΟΥ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"βασιλ εὺς Μαστέαβαρ βασιλέος Γαυου\"><span data-text=\"βασιλ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">[.....]</span><span data-text=\"εὺς\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ΕΥΣ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαστέαβαρ\"><span data-text=\"Μαστέαβαρ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">ΜΑΣΤΕΑΒΑΡ</span></span><span data-text=\"βασιλέος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΒΑΣΙΛΕΟΣ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γαυου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Γαυου\"><span data-text=\"Γαυου\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">ΓΑΥΟΥ</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]...<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Υ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Π[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΕΥ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>].ΕΙΑΝ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>].ΟΥ<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Ε<br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΟΥ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003077_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 03.10.2019: Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic003077_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003077.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 03.10.2019: Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic003077-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003077_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 03.10.2019: Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic003077_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003077_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 03.10.2019: Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic003077_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Preliminary text after Gentili 1956, requiring revision after autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1959.0230 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a>  </li><li> 52.0933 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 39.1033 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 16.0535 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Gentili NSA 1956 96 no.4 fig.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Kontorini 1975 95-98 pl.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001899\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001899</a>  </li><li> Huss 1989 210-211 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001916\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001916</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 2000 263-265 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001812\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001812</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Letters are square in module, regular and neat, with faint serifs at the termination of the strokes. Letters are consistently 9 mm high, except for omicron which is 4-5 mm.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Γ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Γ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Γ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Γ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target